There are some improvements required to build a complete and stable famework:

- Use of Page Object Model in this framework. All locators and methods can be saved in POM classes, independent of test scripts.
- Exception Handling
- Use of Explicit Wait
- Common/helpers folder should have all the generic functionalities like database connectivity, excel functionalities, login, tear down.
- Reporting and logging needs improvement.
- Scheduling the test scripts.
- Documentation
- Code Reusability
